<paragraph pageId="21" pageNumber="36">Type material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="21" pageNumber="36">1 M holotype (ZMH N° A11/13), Tizi Oumalou (36.5102°, 4.3390°), Tizi Ouzou Province, Djurdjura Mountains, Algeria. Paratype: 1 M juv. (ZMH N° A12/13), same location.</paragraph>
